Christmas with the Mantovani Orchestra 320cbr (Big Papi) 1998

By Elaine
I was so excited to get this CD, I originally had the large Record Album purchased way back when which really was worn out from over the years use. The CD was nearly iedenticle to the Record and we have played it daily since receiving it a couple of weeks ago. It will be playing all during our Christmas Celebrations as background music.

For anyone wants pretty much instrumental without a lot of singing this is the CD for you.
